## Landing Page Copy Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the offer, goal, and target audience
- [ ] 2. Map the page structure: above fold → body → CTA
- [ ] 3. Write above fold: headline, subheadline, visual cue
- [ ] 4. Write body: problem → solution → features → proof → CTA
- [ ] 5. Optimize form fields if applicable
- [ ] 6. Test variations of headlines and CTAs

## Key Inputs
- Offer: {{offer}}
- Goal: {{goal}} (sign-up, purchase, lead capture)
- Audience: {{audience}}
- Key Benefits: {{key_benefits}}
- Proof Points: {{proof_points}}
